{
  "title": "Mac OS X 的 Command Line 環境設定",
  "cells": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "data": "<embed id=\"xunlei_com_thunder_helper_plugin_d462f475-c18e-46be-bd10-327458d045bd\" type=\"application/thunder_download_plugin\" height=\"0\" width=\"0\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px;\"><div class=\"title\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 'PT Serif', Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif; line-height: 16px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline;\"><h2 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 'PT Serif', Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', 'Songti SC', 'Hiragino Mincho ProN', serif; line-height: normal; font-size: 2.1em; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(77, 77, 77);\"><a href=\"http://blog.littlelin.info/posts/2014/01/05/mac-os-x-command-line-environment-setup\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration: none;\">Mac OS X 的 Command Line 環境設定</a></h2></div><div class=\"article\" style=\"margin: 1em 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(222, 222, 222); font-family: 'PT Serif', Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', serif; line-height: 1.75; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\"><p style=\"margin: 1.25em 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; -webkit-hyphens: auto;\">筆記一下自已在 Mac OS X 下，針對 Command Line 的相關環境設定。以下操作都是在 Mac OS X Mavericks 10.9.1 版本下的設定記錄。</p><p style=\"margin: 1.25em 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; -webkit-hyphens: auto;\">整體調整後的效果如下圖︰</p><p style=\"margin: 1.25em 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; -webkit-hyphens: auto;\"><img class=\"center\" src=\"quiver-image-url/2BD9801CA1AAFA68070E0044183BC74D.png\" alt=\"iTerm2.png\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 1px solid rgb(212, 212, 212); font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; display: block;\" width=\"764\" height=\"587\"></p><h4 style=\"margin: 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 'PT Serif', Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', 'Songti SC', 'Hiragino Mincho ProN', serif; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-size: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(77, 77, 77);\">1. 安裝 iTerm2</h4><p style=\"margin: 1.25em 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; -webkit-hyphens: auto;\"><a href=\"http://www.iterm2.com/#/section/home\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-bottom-style: dashed; border-bottom-color: rgb(29, 140, 189); font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration: none;\">iTerm2</a>&nbsp;是社群開發出來取代 Mac OS X 內建的 Terminal(終端機) 的好用軟體。有興趣的朋友可以閱讀官網上的<a href=\"http://www.iterm2.com/#/section/features\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-bottom-style: dashed; border-bottom-color: rgb(29, 140, 189); font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration: none;\">Features 頁面</a>，可以對 iTerm2 提供的功能有更多的了解。</p><p style=\"margin: 1.25em 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; -webkit-hyphens: auto;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 'PT Serif', Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', 'Songti SC', 'Hiragino Mincho ProN', serif; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">官網︰</strong><a href=\"http://www.iterm2.com/#/section/home\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-bottom-style: dashed; border-bottom-color: rgb(29, 140, 189); font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration: none;\">http://www.iterm2.com/#/section/home</a><br><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 'PT Serif', Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', 'Songti SC', 'Hiragino Mincho ProN', serif; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">安裝方式︰</strong>下載後解壓縮，將解壓縮出來的檔案，放置到&nbsp;<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 'PT Serif', Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', 'Songti SC', 'Hiragino Mincho ProN', serif; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">/Applications</strong>&nbsp;目錄下即可<br><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 'PT Serif', Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', 'Songti SC', 'Hiragino Mincho ProN', serif; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">安裝後設定︰</strong></p><h5 style=\"margin: 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 'PT Serif', Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', 'Songti SC', 'Hiragino Mincho ProN', serif; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: normal; line-height: inherit; font-size: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(77, 77, 77);\">a. 將 iTerm 設定為 Mac OS 預設的終端機程式</h5><p style=\"margin: 1.25em 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; -webkit-hyphens: auto;\"><img class=\"center\" src=\"quiver-image-url/6028BBB6E22600B42A19FD52A7193E9E.png\" alt=\"Default Term.png\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 1px solid rgb(212, 212, 212); font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; display: block;\" width=\"327\" height=\"342\"></p><h5 style=\"margin: 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 'PT Serif', Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', 'Songti SC', 'Hiragino Mincho ProN', serif; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: normal; line-height: inherit; font-size: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(77, 77, 77);\">b. 字型設定</h5><p style=\"margin: 1.25em 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; -webkit-hyphens: auto;\">我自己滿喜歡微軟推出的 Consolas 字型，所以在安裝完 iTerm2 後，我就將 Consolas 設定為 iTerm2 的預設字型。另外我自己試過不錯的字型還有&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/adobe/source-code-pro\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-bottom-style: dashed; border-bottom-color: rgb(29, 140, 189); font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration: none;\">Adobe Source Code Pro</a>，有興趣的朋友也可以下載安裝試看看。</p><p style=\"margin: 1.25em 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; -webkit-hyphens: auto;\"><img class=\"center\" src=\"quiver-image-url/0E9648178447280467B5BAF508EC8F2A.png\" alt=\"iTerm2.png\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 1px solid rgb(212, 212, 212); font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; display: block;\" width=\"800\" height=\"468\"></p><h5 style=\"margin: 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 'PT Serif', Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', 'Songti SC', 'Hiragino Mincho ProN', serif; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: normal; line-height: inherit; font-size: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(77, 77, 77);\">c. 終端機色碼調整</h5><p style=\"margin: 1.25em 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; -webkit-hyphens: auto;\">我很喜歡 IR_Black 相關佈景主題，所以不管我是在 Visual Studio、VIM 下，都會儘量找尋 IR_Black 的佈景主題來使用。現在使用 iTerm2 當然也不例外，社群有人熱心的將適用於 iTerm2 的 IR_Black 色碼設定，放到 GitHub 上，網址如下︰<a href=\"https://gist.github.com/meqif/1238378\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-bottom-style: dashed; border-bottom-color: rgb(29, 140, 189); font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration: none;\">https://gist.github.com/meqif/1238378</a>。</p><p style=\"margin: 1.25em 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; -webkit-hyphens: auto;\">安裝方式也很簡單，你可以手動將網址中的檔案內容，複製貼上，存成一個 IR_Black.itermcolors 的檔案，或直接使用 wget 指令下載︰</p><blockquote style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0.5em; border-width: 0px 0px 0px 0.5em; border-left-color: rgb(230, 230, 230); font-style: italic; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; quotes: none;\"><p style=\"margin: 1.25em 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; -webkit-hyphens: auto;\">wget&nbsp;<a href=\"https://gist.github.com/meqif/1238378/raw/a8547ad88c698e5ce7391ba5fb35401500e89001/IR_Black.itermcolors\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-bottom-style: dashed; border-bottom-color: rgb(29, 140, 189); font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration: none;\">https://gist.github.com/meqif/1238378/raw/a8547ad88c698e5ce7391ba5fb35401500e89001/IR_Black.itermcolors</a></p></blockquote><p style=\"margin: 1.25em 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; -webkit-hyphens: auto;\">再進入 iTerm2 的 Preferences 做相關色碼設定就可以了。</p><p style=\"margin: 1.25em 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; -webkit-hyphens: auto;\"><img class=\"center\" src=\"quiver-image-url/0FCA82A68BE9436931F6A4C3829A346E.png\" alt=\"iTerm2 色碼設定\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 1px solid rgb(212, 212, 212); font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; display: block;\" width=\"800\" height=\"515\"></p><h4 style=\"margin: 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 'PT Serif', Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', 'Songti SC', 'Hiragino Mincho ProN', serif; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-size: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(77, 77, 77);\">2. Bash 相關設定</h4><p style=\"margin: 1.25em 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; -webkit-hyphens: auto;\">Mac OS X 預設的 Shell 是 Bash，其實社群有個威力很強大的&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/revans/bash-it\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-bottom-style: dashed; border-bottom-color: rgb(29, 140, 189); font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration: none;\">bash-it</a>&nbsp;專案，可供大家快速打造強大的 Bash 環境，有興趣的朋友可以試試。因為小弟也正在研究中，所以本篇暫時不會提到&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/revans/bash-it\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-bottom-style: dashed; border-bottom-color: rgb(29, 140, 189); font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration: none;\">bash-it</a>&nbsp;的使用方式，未來也許會將研究結果更新在本文中，或是另外寫一篇筆記來記錄。</p><h5 style=\"margin: 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 'PT Serif', Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', 'Songti SC', 'Hiragino Mincho ProN', serif; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: normal; line-height: inherit; font-size: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(77, 77, 77);\">a. 使 ls 指令變彩色的</h5><p style=\"margin: 1.25em 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; -webkit-hyphens: auto;\">Mac OS X 預設的設定，在使用 ls 指令，輸出都是黑白的。不會以顏色來表示特殊的檔案格式 (ex: 目錄、symbolic link 等)，這對使用上來說，不太方便，所以我們可以在 ~/.bash_profile 檔加入以下設定，來開啟 ls 的顏色顯示︰</p><blockquote style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0.5em; border-width: 0px 0px 0px 0.5em; border-left-color: rgb(230, 230, 230); font-style: italic; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; quotes: none;\"><p style=\"margin: 1.25em 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; -webkit-hyphens: auto;\">export CLICOLOR=1<br>export LSCOLORS=dxfxcxdxbxegedabagacad</p></blockquote><h5 style=\"margin: 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 'PT Serif', Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', 'Songti SC', 'Hiragino Mincho ProN', serif; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: normal; line-height: inherit; font-size: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(77, 77, 77);\">b. Bash 提示字元(prompt) 調整</h5><p style=\"margin: 1.25em 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; -webkit-hyphens: auto;\">針對 Bash 提示字元的設置，有興趣的朋友可以試看看&nbsp;<a href=\"http://xta.github.io/HalloweenBash/\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-bottom-style: dashed; border-bottom-color: rgb(29, 140, 189); font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration: none;\">Bash Profile Generator</a>&nbsp;這個網站。它主要是透過 UI，供你設定並預覽你想在提示字元上看到的欄位 (ex: 主機名稱、目前所在目錄、使用者名稱等)，然後在頁面最下面顯示你應該如何設定 ~/.bash_profile 檔的建議值。對於學習怎麼設定 Bash 提示字元，算是一個很不錯的網站，推薦給大家。</p><p style=\"margin: 1.25em 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; -webkit-hyphens: auto;\">但這次我不是直接編輯 ~/.bash_profile 檔，而是使用&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/magicmonty/bash-git-prompt\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-bottom-style: dashed; border-bottom-color: rgb(29, 140, 189); font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration: none;\">bash-git-prompt</a>&nbsp;來設定我的提示字元。<a href=\"https://github.com/magicmonty/bash-git-prompt\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-bottom-style: dashed; border-bottom-color: rgb(29, 140, 189); font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration: none;\">bash-git-prompt</a>&nbsp;的特色是，可以在 Bash 提示字元上，顯示目前我所在 Git repository 的分支 (branch)、commit 狀態等資訊。可以提升我們在 Command Line 下使用 Git 的生產力。</p><p style=\"margin: 1.25em 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; -webkit-hyphens: auto;\">安裝方式很簡單，執行以下指令︰</p><blockquote style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0.5em; border-width: 0px 0px 0px 0.5em; border-left-color: rgb(230, 230, 230); font-style: italic; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; quotes: none;\"><p style=\"margin: 1.25em 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; -webkit-hyphens: auto;\">git clone&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/magicmonty/bash-git-prompt.git\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-bottom-style: dashed; border-bottom-color: rgb(29, 140, 189); font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration: none;\">https://github.com/magicmonty/bash-git-prompt.git</a>&nbsp;.bash-git-prompt</p></blockquote><p style=\"margin: 1.25em 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; -webkit-hyphens: auto;\">將相關的 shell script 下載到 ~/.bash-git-prompt 目錄下，然後編輯 ~/.bash_profile 設定檔，加入以下設定，來匯入<a href=\"https://github.com/magicmonty/bash-git-prompt\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-bottom-style: dashed; border-bottom-color: rgb(29, 140, 189); font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration: none;\">bash-git-prompt</a>&nbsp;的設定 shell script︰</p><blockquote style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0.5em; border-width: 0px 0px 0px 0.5em; border-left-color: rgb(230, 230, 230); font-style: italic; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; quotes: none;\"><p style=\"margin: 1.25em 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; -webkit-hyphens: auto;\">source ~/.bash-git-prompt/gitprompt.sh</p></blockquote><p style=\"margin: 1.25em 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; -webkit-hyphens: auto;\">這樣就安裝完成了。不過因為&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/magicmonty/bash-git-prompt\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-bottom-style: dashed; border-bottom-color: rgb(29, 140, 189); font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration: none;\">bash-git-prompt</a>&nbsp;預設的提示字元是 2 行 (可以看官網的抓圖)，而且有些欄位並不是我想要的，所以我調整一下 ~/.bash-git-prompt/gitprompt.sh 檔，檔案內容我放在<a href=\"https://gist.github.com/anonymous/8270381\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-bottom-style: dashed; border-bottom-color: rgb(29, 140, 189); font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration: none;\">https://gist.github.com/anonymous/8270381</a>，調整的部份是 63、64、67、73 行，主要是針對提示字元的欄位做調整而已，主要程式沒有做任何改變。</p><h4 style=\"margin: 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 'PT Serif', Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', 'Songti SC', 'Hiragino Mincho ProN', serif; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-size: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(77, 77, 77);\">小結</h4><p style=\"margin: 1.25em 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; -webkit-hyphens: auto;\">Linux / Mac OS X 最強大的功能之一，就是其完整而豐富的 Command Line 功能，希望我可以在未來整理筆記的過程中，逐步完善我對它的理解。</p><h4 style=\"margin: 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 'PT Serif', Georgia, Times, 'Times New Roman', 'Songti SC', 'Hiragino Mincho ProN', serif; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-size: 19px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(77, 77, 77);\">References</h4><ul style=\"margin: 1.25em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-position: inside; list-style-image: initial;\"><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><a href=\"http://www.iterm2.com/#/section/home\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-bottom-style: dashed; border-bottom-color: rgb(29, 140, 189); font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration: none;\">iTerm2 官網</a></li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><a href=\"https://github.com/magicmonty/bash-git-prompt\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-bottom-style: dashed; border-bottom-color: rgb(29, 140, 189); font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration: none;\">bash-git-prompt 官網</a></li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><a href=\"http://xta.github.io/HalloweenBash/\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-bottom-style: dashed; border-bottom-color: rgb(29, 140, 189); font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant-ligatures: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-caps: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration: none;\">Bash Profile Generator</a></li></ul></div>"
    }
